[SHORT DESC]
Lowers target's accuracy by 1 stage.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage and has a 100% chance to lower the target's accuracy by one stage.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Mud-Slap has little competitive use, mainly because there are many more powerful options. Although there is a 100% chance to lower the target's accuracy, this effect can be negated by the foe simply switching out.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/earth_power">Earth Power</a> is a more powerful option.</p>